			<h3 ><a href="#p11" rel="nofollow"><!-- google_ad_section_start -->Re: Alfredo Simon - Should he be shut down?<!-- google_ad_section_end --></a></h3>
			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=11&amp;sid=24903fbd09914fbdc32270e6cc9f7859#p11"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=11&amp;sid=24903fbd09914fbdc32270e6cc9f7859#p11" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#2</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2&amp;sid=24903fbd09914fbdc32270e6cc9f7859" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">Jordan Tuwiner</a></strong> &raquo; September 5th, 2010, 1:09 am <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

			<div id="explanation11" style="display:none" >
					<form action="" method="post">
						<fieldset>
							<textarea name="comment_text" cols="60" rows="5"></textarea><br />
							<input name="comment_to_id" type="hidden" value="2" />
							<input name="Submit" type="submit" class="button1" value="Submit" />
						</fieldset>
					</form>
